metadata.name: Path of Unknown Artists
metadata.description:
Immersive video created in virtual reality, about the path of unknown artists. Collaboration of two authors.

Format: mp4,  
Dimensions: 1280 x 720 px, 
Duration: 0:44.  
Unique Edition 1/1


Unknown Artists 

To trudge the road of happy destiny … 
It’s often a lonely task. 
Off the beaten path 
Is where the winners are at. 
We forget a path to the future. 
For those afraid of the dark. 
That is where our little light will glow. 
Now the show will begin to start. 
When we push ahead of fearfulness, 
Our little light will begin to grow. 
Welcome to the undiscovered path… 
Of the artists who are Unknown.


IrinaStepArt
